data.description: Motivated Seller.  Beautifully updated home with ideal layout in popular Stonebridge Ranch.  This 4 bedroom, 3.1 bath is light and bright with plantation shutters, extensive crown moulding, and the most versatile floorplan. All bedrooms are down.  Upgrades include all new blonde hardwood flooring, 5 inch baseboards, entire house repainted, all new lighting, on trend hardware, mirrors and faucets, quartz countertops in secondary bathrooms, dining room feature wall, & an iron front door. Roof and ACs are less than 6 years old. Stonebridge Ranch is a fabulous community with miles of walking and biking trails, the beach club, aquatics center, tennis courts, public golf course and private country club. All of this proximate to Sam Rayburn Tollway, US-75 and all restaurants & shopping.
